data.description: Picturesque single family home in highly desirable Vistas neighborhood of Sparks! Welcome home to this fantastic 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home that enjoys 2,308 square feet. Situated on a .2-acre lot and surrounded lush green trees that provide plenty of privacy for you and guests. This home offers an open floorplan that flows from room to room, giving everyone their own space but bringing everyone together in the heart of the home. A gorgeous kitchen ensures the chef of the family has everything they need to craft your favorite meals. The backyard is a true oasis with a jacuzzi, covered patio, large grassy area for little ones and pets to run and stretch their legs and so much more. Make this home your own, book your private showing today!
